, upper panels). We therefore characterized these cells using a tetramer-based enrichment strategy.      ,      Distinct populations of tetramer      CD8      T cells were detected after enrichment in all 7 HLA-B*15      patients with chronic HDV/HBV infection (patients 13, 14, 16, 17, 18, 21, and 23) (

